## sveltin prepare

Get all the dependencies from the `package.json` file

### Synopsis

Initialize the Sveltin project getting all depencencies from the package.json file.

It wraps (npm|pnpm|yarn) install.

By default, sveltin uses `pnpm` as package manager. You can choose npm or yarn simply passing it via the â€“-package-manager flag.

```bash
sveltin prepare [flags]
```

### Options

```bash
  -h, --help                     help for prepare
  -p, --package-manager string   The name of the your preferred package manager. (default "pnpm")
  -u, --update                   Update dependencies
```

